# Interface KeywordMatchInterface

Information about a matched keyword.

Contains the name of the keyword group that matched and the specific keyword that was found.

interface KeywordMatchInterface {  
groupName: string;  
keyword: string;  
}

Name of the keyword group that matched.

The keyword that was matched.
